## 验证

- `scripts/check-consistency.sh` — C6 verifies `state/AGENTS.md` exists;
  C1/C2 may also touch `state/iteration.md` for methodology detection.
- `scripts/check-stuck.sh` (if Q4 includes 卡死检测) — reads the
  `progress_signature` history from `iteration.md` front matter for stuck
  detection.
